    Description

    Fast paced 3v3 & 5v5 MOBA and Battle Royale made for mobile! Play online with friends or solo across a variety of PvP arena game modes in under three minutes.


    Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful super abilities, star powers and gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious arena locations within the MOBA Brawliverse!




    ◉ BATTLE IN MULTIPLE GAME MODES:


    ▶ Gem Grab (3v3,5v5): Team up for real time 3v3 and 5v5 MOBA arena PvP battles against online players from across the world. Team up to battle and out strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.


    ▶ Showdown (solo/duo): A MOBA battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo, be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest MOBA PvP battle royale yet. Winner takes it all!


    ▶ Brawl Ball (3v3,5v5): It's a whole new brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.


    ▶ Bounty (3v3,5v5): Battle to take out opponents and earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!


    ▶ Heist (3v3,5v5): Protect your team’s safety and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the arena to sneak, blast, battle and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.


    ▶ Special MOBA Events: Limited time special MOBA PvE and PvP arena battle game modes.


    ▶ Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!




    ◉ UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS:


    Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful super abilities, star powers and gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skin.
    A fast paced battle royale MOBA made for mobile. Unlock and collect new, powerful "brawlers", each with a signature attack and super ability.



    ◉ BRAWL PASS:


    Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.



    ◉ BECOME THE STAR PLAYERS


    Battle to climb the local and regional PvP leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest MOBA brawler of them all! Join or start your own MOBA club with fellow players online to share tips and battle together. Climb to the top of the PvP leaderboards in global and local rankings.




    ◉ CONSTANTLY EVOLVING MOBA


    Look out for new "brawlers", skins, maps, special events and game modes in the future. Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins. Enjoy PVP battles solo or with friends online.
    New PVP and PVE events and game modes daily. Player designed maps offer challenging new terrain to master.




    Please note!
    Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 9 years of age to play or download Brawl Stars.

    luckiest person in the world , 06/28/2024

    This game is so annoying

    I play this game a lot. It can be fun, but sometimes I hate this game. There always has to be someone to ruin the fun. The most common issue is Bad Randoms. For example, I literally played the championship challenge and I got star player every single time, with around 2 or 3 deaths and 5 or 6 kills on average. Meanwhile, my teammates have around 5 to 4 deaths with 1 or 0 kills. Only very rarely do you actually get some kinda random that are just not on my trophy level or are power 5 or something like that. Another problem is the wintraders and mastery farmers. Even the top players in the WORLD wintrade. Then they spam the dislike and clown pin with the “X” spray. Mastery farmers are also really annoying. In fact, I really hope they lose every single match so they don’t get mastery. These people get so much resources just by using and autoclicker and waiting for a few hours. Teamers are a problem too, but they aren’t as bad as the other issues.
    Suggestions: Straight up ban the dislike and clown pin and anything related to it. The only use the have is to be toxic.
    Another suggestion is to add a report button to ALL gamemodes. There should also be a “record” button in the battle logs and somehow give Supercell proof that you are not just reporting because you are mad.
    PLEASE FIX THESE ISSUES

    charlesazoid , 09/17/2024

    My favorite mobile game but needs some work

    This is a great game overall. Progression is good and so is gameplay. There are a few problems I have with the game and suggestions to make the problems a bit better. 1: I find it annoying when your in a gem grab and your team has dominated the whole time You have all the gems but then one guy kills your one guy who has all the gems and they lose them all and the guy who killed them runs home and wins the match. My suggestion is make the person who died retain say, half the gems when they died 2: I feel that some gadgets are a little OP such as colts homing one, dynamites stun or emz push. As a very Edgar main all the push ones are annoying. But I feel like that is fair too make Edgar not the most annoying brawler to fight. I don’t have a suggestion for this one but I just wanted to list it 3: I feel like way you upgrade brawlers is too expensive. Please maybe make it so that you spend power points on brawlers and coins on gadgets, star powers, gear, and hypercharge. Also consider lowering the price of ticket buying in the star road. 4: please remove the possibility of bots in ranked matches. I once fought two of the same bot in one match and one was underleveled. love this game and I hope you continue development of it in the years to come. Yours truly- a fan p.s I understand that such a massive game empire like supercell is not going to read this but if they do I would love it if you considered some of the things I’ve suggested
